<item>
            <title>[LU-8548] MDS crash during DNE2 testing with Lustre 2.9</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8548</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I attached the kern log that captured the OOM that happened while running mdtest with the directory striped across 16 MDTs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Power8 clients running 2.8.56 and back end servers running the same. This OOM happened while running mdtest with the directory striped across 16 MDTs.</environment>
        <key id="39127">LU-8548</key>
            <summary>MDS crash during DNE2 testing with Lustre 2.9</summary>
